Package: behamoth
Type: Package
Title: provide a helper function to use for setting up ggplot themes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: BENNOUR Mohamed Hsin
Maintainer: BENNOUR Mohamed Hsin <hsin.bennour@gmail.com>
Description: For elegant graphs sometimes you need to set up various components
    in the gplot2 theme to a specific value, this package sets these components to the desired value for you once you specify the value you desire.   
    Specifically this package targets the values of the background color and removing all grids and ticks if the user chooses to. 
